Our ValueOur approach has revolutionized the world of after-hours triage. We provide solutions tailored to the needs of your patients. Experience our difference by partnering with IntellaTriage today.

Who We AreAt IntellaTriage, our mission is to act as an extension of each client by using a tailored approach to deliver compassionate, around-the-clock care through the clinical expertise of our virtual registered nurses.

Our ApproachAfter-hours care shouldnt be an afterthought. IntellaTriage provides high quality nurse triage services at any time of day. By partnering with us, healthcare providers reduce nurse burnout and improve patient experience.
In The NewsStay up to date with the latest news about our services, expansions, and hirings.
Nurse Burnout & RetentionA customized, after-hours solutions can result in increased job satisfaction and performance, a better patient experience, and a boost to your organizations bottom line.

ProvidersIntellaTriage provides nurse-based triage services for physician groups, ACOs, health systems, and more. Our solutions are tailored to the needs of each client, ensuring that your patients receive the highest quality of care, day or night.

Health PlansMany insurers and health plans can benefit from nurse advice line services to minimize member cost. Provide instant, comprehensive care for your population by partnering with IntellaTriage.
After-Hours CareThis specialized service utilizes highly trained registered nurses to help lighten and manage a healthcare organizations call load.

Patient ExperienceThe best patient engagement solution delivers the highest quality personalized care. It also can provide valuable information back to the caregivers about what truly motivates patients to engage in their care.
CareersIts More Than a Job. Its a Calling!

Nurse Advice LineIntellaTriage equips your patients with 24/7 access to an advice line staffed by registered nurses. Our experienced team members answer calls, direct patients to appropriate care, and dispense appropriate medical guidance at any time, day or night.

Hospice + Home HealthIntellaTriage provides after-hours, nurse-based triage services for hospice, home health, and palliative care patients. Our 24/7 service will improve your patients experience and reduce staff burnout.
Patient EngagementImprove patient outcomes, close gaps in treatment, and reduce readmission by taking advantage of IntellaTriages patient engagement services.
Nurse TriageHealth problems arent restricted to a 9 to 5 workday. With an after-hours nurse triage service, you can be there for your patients 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.
